Collection of apps for Windows that will help you in learning the various bible verses or passages.

BibleVerseWidget - Displays selected or random verses from the 1671 King James Bible (KJV) in passive flashcard manner that floats on your screen and speaks using Text to Speech.
![Alt text](https://www.github.com/DevBuilder47/BibleApps/blob/main/BibleWidget/bibleversewidget.png "Bible Verse Widget main screen")
